9.4.10 Drift Observatory Integration (F-6.5.16)
Section 9.4 supplies IDDO with:
• Confidence distribution snapshots
 • Ambiguity category distribution
 • Structural order violation rate
 • Dual-branch frequency rate
 • Confidence reversal rate
Drift threshold:
≥10% absolute deviation
 ≥250 cases
 ≥7 sustained days
Baseline adaptation frozen during:
• Declared surge periods
 • Structural anomaly windows
Baseline establishment requires:
• Minimum 30 stable days
 • Minimum case volume threshold
 • Variance within acceptable range
Surge periods excluded from baseline formation.

